DOCUMENT();        # This should be the first executable line in the problem.

loadMacros(
  "PGstandard.pl",
  "PGchoicemacros.pl",
  "PGcourse.pl"
);

TEXT(beginproblem());
$showPartialCorrectAnswers = 1;

$a = random(3,4,1);
$b = random(2,5,1);
$c = random(2,5,1);
$d = random(2,5,1);
$e = random(2,5,1);

$b1 = $b**(2*$a);
TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
The expression \(\sqrt[$a]{$b1 g^$c y^$d} \sqrt{$b1 g^$c y^$d}\) equals
\(kg^ry^s\) $BR where r, the exponent of g, is:
\{ans_rule(20) \}
$BR
EOT

$ans = $c*(2+$a)/(2*$a);
ANS(num_cmp($ans));

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
and s, the exponent of y, is:
\{ans_rule(20) \}
$BR
EOT

$ans = $d*(2+$a)/(2*$a);
ANS(num_cmp($ans));
TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
and k, the leading coefficient is:
\{ans_rule(20)\}
$BR
EOT

$ans = $b**(2+$a);
ANS(num_cmp($ans));
ENDDOCUMENT();        # This should be the last executable line in the problem.

